<md>
#### Filter Commands (`-command`)
Modifier for `-command_list`. Filters the output to show only the specified commands.

**Syntax:** `-command <cmd1|cmd2|...>`

```
<@|TEST -command_list -command <edit|manage>
---end---
```
</md>